data.description: Spacious move in ready split foyer! Large family room with soaring vaulted ceilings and gas fireplace! Kitchen features updated appliances and ample counter space and cabinet storage! Oversized master on upper level with walk in closet and private full bath. Two secondary bedrooms and hall full bath complete the upper level. Lower level features a second living room space, bedroom and full bathroom. Roof and hot water heater are only TWO years old! Just minutes to Douglasville shopping and dining and easy access to I-20 and right off 92.
